{"tid":1228473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位兄弟姊妹，請好好珍惜生命","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:19:00.000Z","uid":49479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3412da4c91d9f2124827797f2dbe6cee09d802","tid":1228473,"uid":49479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pddKiV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpddKiV0.png&h=7b4c32ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烈士已經犧牲咗，悲劇無人想<br />\n有人會話唔值得<br />\n有人會話咁做無用<br />\n甚至有人會話一齊以死相諫<br />\n<br />\n我想你哋知道，烈士以死相諫為嘅係乜？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係香港，係我哋每一個香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n佢唔係要做英雄，佢係想以死去控訴<br />\n「全面撤回送中，我們不是暴動，釋放學生傷者，林鄭下台，Help Hong Kong」<br />\n「反送中No Extradition To China」<br />\n<br />\n悲劇始終都發生咗，值唔值得/有無用已經唔再重要，重要嘅係我哋唔可以俾佢白白犧牲<br />\n大家唔好再分黨分派，聽日開始我哋只有一個身份，就係香港人！<br />\n目的就係要撒回送中，釋放義士，制裁一班濫用暴力嘅黑警，重新定義612 唔係暴動！<br />\n而我哋需要做嘅唔係要再一個手足犧牲以死控訴，我哋需要嘅係每一個香港人嘅力量，一齊走出來完成烈士嘅遺願，行佢未行完嘅路，一個都不能少！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">They can't kill us all!</span><br />\n<br />\n大家要團結！珍惜生命先有能力繼續抗爭落去，香港人需要你，需要你哋每一個！唔要再有手足流多一滴血！香港加油！"},{"pid":"793eda33a43e2d08dc826262260527a345420700","tid":1228473,"uid":49479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"電話熱線服務: <br />\n1. 香港紅十字會 ：3628-1180 <br />\n(設中、英文)<br />\n6月15-16日：2-10pm<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Xi7gwR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Xi7gwR&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe24bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=8adb847b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Xi7gwR</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 生命熱線 2382-0000<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sps.org.hk/?a=group&amp;id=hotline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sps.org.hk%2F%3Fa%3Dgroup%26id%3Dhotline&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe24bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=61e66d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sps.org.hk/?a=group&amp;id=hotline</a> <b